						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/lit-hub-daily-january-21-2025/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">Lit Hub Daily: January 21, 2025</h7>
			</a>
			





 	RESPONDING TO THE SECOND TRUMP ADMINISTRATION: Kim Kelly on the how-tos and DOs and DON’Ts of mutual aid • Madeline...			
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<li id="custom_ads-24" class="widget Custom_Ads"><div class="htlad-LH_PP_F"></div></li>
					<div class='htlad-LH_HP_ALB'></div>
		
	
